title: Elif Ağca Yarar
summary: Nedime Elif Ağca Yarar (born February 10, 1984 in Ankara), also known as Nedime Elif Ağca Öner, is a retired national level Turkish volleyball player who last played for Fenerbahçe. She is 186 cm (6 ft 1 in) tall and plays as setter. She studied at Marmara University.
